title: Emerging Markets Waver Amid Thin Holiday Trading, Fed Anxiety
description: Emerging-market assets were little changed on Tuesday as traders weighed the recent optimism toward the asset class against a firmer US dollar and thinner trading volumes due to holidays in major markets.
